org.sbml.jsbml.util.filters.Filter

Packages that use Filter
org.sbml.jsbml Pure Java implementation of the data structures to represent all SBML constructs. 
org.sbml.jsbml.util.filters Filter are useful to decide whether or not to accept a certain item.

 class AssignmentVariableFilter

 class NameFilter
          This filter only accepts instances of NamedSBase with the name as given in the constructor of this object.
 class OrFilter

 class SBOFilter

 class SpeciesReferenceFilter
          This is a special NameFilter that allows users to search for a SimpleSpeciesReference that refers to a Species with the given identifier attribute.
